<br>
Changing it to swarm pets?  No please, copied over from too many other classes, and swarm pets are just fucking annoying.<br>
<br>
Shield of notes seems pretty nice, no complaints there.<br>
<br>
Bellow upgrades... havent bought the last ones, not gonna buy this one. <br>
<br>
Improved CS/CA is nice enough I suppose.  The shielding or whatever no offhand riposte has potential I suppose, unless its 100aa to max for a 50% chance... 25 for a 100% chance would be nice, I might actually buy it at that.<br>
<br>
Some of the stuff seems nice, like shield of notes, perm illusion, perm eb, yadda yadda (even tho its for everyone).<br>
<br>
Problem I see is with things like crits... it's going to help everyone way more than us.  Add to the fact that our weapons are by no means significantly better than anyone elses (as has been pointed out before) and the gap between our dps and everyone elses just widens... and widens.<br>
<br>
So 2 things I would like to see added to our list is an upgrade to HA, and maybe some sort of (as listed before) 4x +damage activated disc-type ability that will let us do some burst DPS.<br>
<br>
Maybe something like.... 4 4 4 4 4 for a clone-ability of HA that adds 150 or 200% of whatever HA did for our ability to double attack.  i.e. something better than HA oringially was again, to do something about ending this growing of the gap.  No need to get greedy, but another HA exact clone isn't going to help enough.  Feel free to dissect that percentage or cost, but I think something in that general idea would help stem the growing gap that we speak of so often.<br>
<br>
And who knows on the disc thing, as long as we can do some actual meaningful burst dps for a little, it doesn't have to be godlike, I'd probably settle for a clone of rogue 4x disc <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
